    The Roman number format for the input is : XXII
    The Roman number format for the input is : XXXIII
    The Roman number format for the input is : XLIV
    The Roman number format for the input is : LV
    The Roman number format for the input is : LXVI
    The Roman number format for the input is : LXXVII
    The Roman number format for the input is : LXXXVIII
